\ls3\ilvl0
\f4\fs22 \AppleTypeServices \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f2\b\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 The Glass Transparency:
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  The glass exit doors on your background layer should be drawn with roughly 20% opacity.\
\ls3\ilvl0
