\f2\b\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 The Layer Order Saves the Day:
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  Because your script composites the guard 
\f6\i \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 under
\f1\i0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  the foreground layers, when the guard stands at pixel 1350 (inside, but right behind the glass doors), the 20% opacity glass layer is drawn 
\f6\i \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 on top of him
\f1\i0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 . This automatically gives his sprite a realistic reflective glass look.\
\ls3\ilvl0
